This is the interface part of Moonlight Creator.

Subdirectories are:

  graphics/        The base implementation for the windowing system, opengl
                   initialization, event handling.

  koala/           The widget library, based on OpenGL.

  kw/              The high level widget API, used by dialog boxes.

koalagui is a library linked into the main executable.

/SR, March 31 1998 (the mozilla day!)
